{"tha-ap276:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap276:0.2":"Suvannabibbohanavagga ","tha-ap276:0.3":"Abbhanjanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap276:1.1":"“Kondannassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap276:1.2":"vitaragassa tadino; ","tha-ap276:1.3":"Akasasamacittassa, ","tha-ap276:1.4":"nippapancassa jhayino. ","tha-ap276:2.1":"Sabbamohativattassa, ","tha-ap276:2.2":"sabbalokahitesino; ","tha-ap276:2.3":"Abbhanjanam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap276:2.4":"dvipadindassa tadino. ","tha-ap276:3.1":"Aparimeyye ito kappe, ","tha-ap276:3.2":"abbhanjanamadam tada; ","tha-ap276:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap276:3.4":"abbhanjanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap276:4.1":"Ito pannarase kappe, ","tha-ap276:4.2":"cirappo nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap276:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap276:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap276:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap276:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap276:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap276:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma abbhanjanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap276:7.1":"Abbhanjanadayakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}